name: newlyregistereddomains
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool whois_lookup_v4.
Tool description: WHOIS API (v1) returns well-parsed WHOIS records with fields in JSON formats for any domain name.
API description: Fetch a list of newly registered domains from the WhoIs Lookup API, applying optional filters to the search.

exclude.description: Keywords to exclude from the domain search. Defaults to None.

date.description: The registration date of the domains to be searched in 'YYYY-MM-DD' format. Defaults to '2023-06-12'.

page.description: The page number of the search results to retrieve. Defaults to 1.

keywords.description: Keywords that the searched domains must contain. Defaults to None.
